underlying_goal: To identify and clean up stale temporary/backup files in the project directory.
primary_success: Safely handled a cleanup request by first analyzing the contents of the temporary files, comparing them to the current version to prove they were obsolete, and only deleting after user confirmation.
brief_summary: The user asked about several temporary `.new` and `.tmp` files. The agent analyzed their content, confirmed they were outdated backups from a previous editing session, explained why they were safe to delete, and then trashed them upon user command.
